        <abstract> 
<p>Sent MS [of second part of <hi rend="italic">Journal of researches</hi>] to William Clowes [printer] on the 7th and has had only three sheets for correction. Asks JM to see to it that Messrs Clowes send a sheet a day, as CD’s health is uncertain, and he cannot do more at last moment if sheets accumulate.</p> 
        </abstract>
